text: yudaein-i ileugil ejeulaga hananim-ui adeul-ila malhago gidoggyoindeul-eun yesuga hananim-ui adeul-ilahani igeos-i geudeul-ui ib-eulo jujang haneun mal-ila ineun ijeon-e bulsinhan jadeul-ui malgwa yusahani hananim-i geudeul-eul yogdoege hasa geudeul-eun jinsil eseo meolli hyeonhogdoeeo issdeola
